@node "history" "History"
@next "Main"
@prev "author"
  History
  ~~~~~~~
  01-04-96 :  V1.0  First release
 
  04-04-96 :  V1.1  A few stupid bugs fixed

  25-04-96 :  V1.2  Added a tooltype for a default destination
                    Made a few improvements
                    Should now work with a 68000
  
  29-04-96 :  V1.3  Now detects MultiUser AFS partitions
                    Added a tooltype for the buffer copy size
                    Can launch MUI preferences
                    Nicer icons ;)  

  03-07-96 :  V1.4  Now detects AFS user version partitions;
                    Sorry it took so long, but using the pro
                    version, I didn't know the dos type identifier.
                    Thanks for your mail Mr Dahlberg ;)

  05-09-96 :  V1.41 Minor improvements suggested by Michaël Schewior
  
  23-12-96 :  V1.5  The program now updates periodically the device list.
                    That improvement may be usefull for people using 
                    removable devices such as ZIP drives.
                    Once again, that improvement was suggested by
                    Michaël Schewior.
                    Also added a simple Installer script.

  15-05-97 :  V1.6  This new release includes a new tooltype to avoid
                    the testing of given devices. A swedish version of
                    the program and of this guide is included (thanks
                    to Henrik Nilsson and Johan Alfredsson).

@endnode

